classes.json---- saves all the classes registered
get.py---- handles the generate and export timetable, it generates and eports the timetable in pdf, 
            in downloads dir of the user and gets more additional rules from rules.py
main.py----- main page, runs the main app, gui, etc
mc.py----- handles manage classes button, lets user to add, remove, and edit classes registered
msc.json----- holds the data for manage teacher's schedule, all the classesteacher is assigned 
              in and number of their periods in hat class per week
mt.py----- hndles maage teachers, allows add, remove, edit teachers, and manage teacher's schedule
mts.py----- this manages the manage teacher's schedule, by taking data from teach_dat.json, and 
            sores the new schedule in msc.json
rules.py ----- holds the rules for generating the timetable, such that no teacher can have more 
               two classes at one time, and cca, and mpt, and lab classes
s.py----- this manages the settings button, in which it has about us, version, and help
teach_dat.json----- holds the data for teacher's name and the subjects they teach
version.txt----- holds the version of the app, and is shown in settings when user clicks version,
                 and also helps for updating the app when there is a new version, by comparing 
                 the version in this file with the version in the github repo
                                                       